#: ../../source/overview.rst:2
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:5
msgid "What is EDAI?"
msgstr "什么是 EDAI？"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:7
msgid ""
"EDAI is a terminal-based interactive environment that bridges the gap "
"between natural language and EDA (Electronic Design Automation) tools. It"
" provides an IPython shell augmented with:"
msgstr ""
"EDAI 是一个基于终端的交互式环境，弥合了自然语言与 EDA（电子设计自动化）工具之间的鸿沟。"
"它提供了一个增强的 IPython shell，具备以下能力："

#: ../../source/overview.rst:11
msgid ""
"A **large language model agent** that understands your design intent and "
"translates it into executable EDA commands."
msgstr ""
"**大语言模型智能体**，能够理解您的设计意图并将其转换为可执行的 EDA 命令。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:13
msgid ""
"A **built-in Tcl interpreter** that understands 180+ EDA commands across "
"subsystems such as floorplanning, placement, CTS, routing, STA, power "
"analysis, DRC, and more."
msgstr ""
"**内置 Tcl 解释器**，支持 180 多条 EDA 命令，涵盖布局规划、布局布线、时钟树综合、时序分析、功耗分析、设计规则检查等子系统。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:16
msgid ""
"A **simulation backend** that lets you explore the full workflow without "
"requiring an actual EDA license or tool installation."
msgstr ""
"**模拟后端**，让您无需真实的 EDA 许可证或工具安装即可探索完整工作流程。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:19
msgid ""
"EDAI is designed for digital chip design workflows where engineers need "
"to quickly prototype flows, experiment with tool settings, or learn an "
"EDA toolchain through conversational interaction."
msgstr ""
"EDAI 专为数字芯片设计工作流程而设计，工程师可以通过对话式交互快速原型化流程、实验工具设置或学习 EDA 工具链。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:24
msgid "How it Works"
msgstr "工作原理"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:26
msgid ""
"When you start EDAI, you enter an IPython shell with three input modes, "
"automatically detected:"
msgstr ""
"启动 EDAI 后，您将进入一个 IPython shell，系统会自动检测三种输入模式："

#: ../../source/overview.rst:32
msgid "**Tcl commands**"
msgstr "**Tcl 命令**"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:30
msgid ""
"If your input looks like a valid EDA Tcl command (e.g., ``read_liberty "
"-path ./lib.lib``), it is routed directly to the built-in Tcl interpreter"
" for execution."
msgstr ""
"如果您的输入看起来像一个有效的 EDA Tcl 命令（例如 ``read_liberty -path ./lib.lib``），"
"它将被直接路由到内置的 Tcl 解释器执行。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:37
msgid "**Python code**"
msgstr "**Python 代码**"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:35
msgid ""
"If your input can be parsed as valid Python (e.g., "
"``print(sta.worst_slack)``), it is executed in the IPython namespace and "
"the result is displayed."
msgstr ""
"如果您的输入可被解析为有效的 Python 代码（例如 ``print(sta.worst_slack)``），"
"它将在 IPython 命名空间中执行并显示结果。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:42
msgid "**Natural language**"
msgstr "**自然语言**"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:40
msgid ""
"Everything else is sent to the LLM agent, which interprets your intent, "
"selects the appropriate Tcl command, and returns the result."
msgstr ""
"其他所有输入将被发送到 LLM 智能体，智能体会解释您的意图，选择合适的 Tcl 命令，并返回结果。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:44
msgid ""
"This triage happens automatically on every line, so you can mix all three"
" styles freely in a single session."
msgstr ""
"这种分流机制在每一行输入时自动发生，因此您可以在同一会话中自由混用这三种方式。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:48
msgid "Target Audience"
msgstr "目标用户"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:50
msgid "**Digital design engineers** running RTL-to-GDS flows."
msgstr "**数字设计工程师**，运行 RTL 到 GDS 的流程。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:51
msgid "**EDA tool application engineers** developing and debugging tool scripts."
msgstr "**EDA 工具应用工程师**，开发和调试工具脚本。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:53
msgid ""
"**Students and researchers** learning EDA toolchains through "
"conversational interaction."
msgstr ""
"**学生和研究人员**，通过对话式交互学习 EDA 工具链。"

#: ../../source/overview.rst:55
msgid "**Flow automation engineers** prototyping new design flows quickly."
msgstr "**流程自动化工程师**，快速原型化新的设计流程。"
